# meta-Qt6-custom Layer

This layer contains custom Qt6 recipe and configuration for Yocto-based embedded Linux system.  
It is mainly used for Raspberry Pi targets running Qt Quick (QML) applications.

## Adding the Layer

```bash
bitbake-layers add-layer meta-Qt6-custom
```

## Dependencies

```
meta-qt6
poky
meta-openembedded
```

## Contents

```
conf/              # Layer and distro configuration
recipes-core/      # Custom image recipe (my-core-image.bb)
recipes-qt/        # Qt application recipes and service files
```

## Usage

```bash
source oe-init-build-env
bitbake my-core-image
```

